# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# THEIR CODE. Cloned, pinned, never edited, never committed.
# The two-repository principle (plan Rem 15.2): our delta lives in
# patches/, not in a fork. Committing external/ would bury a
# ~400-line contribution inside a 100k-line diff and make rebasing
# onto a new PhysicsNeMo release into archaeology.
# Reproduced instead by: clone at the commit in environment.md,
# then run patches/apply.sh
# ---------------------------------------------------------------
external/

